## 5. Choropleth Map (Optional)

```python
latest_data = df[df['date'] == df['date'].max()]

fig = px.choropleth(latest_data, 
                    locations="iso_code", 
                    color="total_cases", 
                    hover_name="location", 
                    title="Global COVID-19 Total Cases",
                    color_continuous_scale=px.colors.sequential.Plasma)

fig.show()
```

